# Coalesce the maintainer's two personal GitHub accounts (suppledigital
# and corporatebishal) onto the canonical `getcodetta` identity so the
# project's contributor list shows one human maintainer + Claude as a
# co-author, not three separate humans. Claude's Co-Authored-By
# attribution is intentionally preserved — it's accurate and useful.
#
# Format reference: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitmailmap
#   <canonical-name> <canonical-email> <commit-name> <commit-email>
#
# After pushing this file, GitHub re-reads it within ~24 hours and
# rebuilds the contributor list. `git log --use-mailmap` reflects the
# remapping immediately for local tooling.

